Sounds good, but what's with the no seeders? 

This was uploaded over 17 hours ago.

I guess I'll check back in later or tomorrow to see if you're seeding it yet.

Be somewhat reserved and suspicious when you see the Pirate Bay tracker saying there are 0 seeders.

I have noticed this problem on my torrents and other people's torrents when they are first uploaded.   Quite often, even though we are "Force" seeding, the tracker will report 0 seeders, even though I am seeding.

So, my advice when you see 0 seeders is to download the torrent, and let your bit torrent client figure it out.

You might just be pleasantly surprised that someone is seeding the torrent.

-DogNo7
